NORDIC radio frequency core repository, plus unit testing programs.

nrf24l01p and nrf905 are currently supported. There is an implem for
nrf2401a, not tested.

Also, there is a set of functions to program NRF chipsets independtly
of the actual hardware.

src: source common to all projects (nrfxxx.c, spi, uart)
snrf: serial to nrf. contains both codes and schematics.
unit/bw: bandwidth related tests
unit/range: used to test the emission / reception range
unit/simple: do not remember, but must be something simple
